author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
After a nine year hiatus as a solo artist, Glenn Hughes is to release a new album this September and I'm reviewing its title track, "Chosen". Glenn is not just a legend, he's a good friend and someone I've always admired. I hope you enjoy. 

You can watch the video in full here: https://youtu.be/t-fj5sl_Rqc?si=9MJW9OipzBd-5UBj

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is available now: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

title: Why Glenn Hughes is a Legend
